Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的雲南茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的抹茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐  你之前在這家店裡說我擁有技術對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼技術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我來說嗎  推理的技術…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是偵探  而是推理作家才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼令你這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是福爾摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意我劇透一些福爾摩斯的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我不介意
